            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EJustice%20protects%20a%20person's%20equal%20rights.%20Whether%20rich%20or%20poor%2C%20born%20or%20unborn%2C%20educated%20or%20illiterate%2C%20all%20people%20are%20made%20in%20the%20image%20of%20God%20and%20deserve%20equal%20protection%20and%20peace.%20%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EDavid%20prayed%20for%20his%20son%20Solomon%20to%20be%20endowed%20with%20justice%20(Psalm%2072%3A1).%20In%20practical%20terms%2C%20this%20prayer%20was%20asking%20the%20Lord%20to%20help%20Solomon%20%22defend%20the%20poor%2C%20to%20rescue%20the%20children%20of%20the%20needy%2C%20and%20to%20crush%20their%20oppressors%22%20(v.%204).%20Additionally%2C%20David%20prayed%20for%20Solomon%20to%20have%20%22pity%20for%20the%20weak%20and%20the%20needy%22%20(v.%2013)%20and%20to%20%22save%20them%20from%20oppression%20and%20from%20violence%22%20(vv.%2013-14).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20secret%20to%20obtaining%20justice%20is%20instilling%20in%20people%20a%20respect%20for%20the%20sanctity%20of%20blood%2C%20%22for%20the%20life%20of%20any%20creature%20is%20in%20its%20blood%22%20(Leviticus%2017%3A11).%20When%20we%20see%20how%20precious%20blood%20is%20to%20God%2C%20we%20will%20be%20concerned%20about%20its%20senseless%20shedding.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20ignorant%2C%20foolish%20man%20really%20cares%20nothing%20for%20the%20blood%20of%20another%20as%20long%20as%20his%20blood%20is%20not%20being%20shed!%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20man%20of%20wisdom%20is%20broken%20by%20the%20shedding%20of%20innocent%20blood%20that%20offends%20God%20and%20His%20sense%20of%20justice.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EStand%20up%20for%20innocent%20blood!%20In%20that%20way%20you%20are%20showing%20you%20love%20justice%2C%20just%20as%20you%20love%20the%20God%20of%20justice.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
