            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EIsaiah%2060%3A1-62%3A5%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_60_1%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2260%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EIsaiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E60%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EFuture%20Glory%20for%20Jerusalem%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BArise%2C%20Jerusalem!%20Let%20your%20light%20shine%20for%20all%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EFor%20the%20glory%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20rises%20to%20shine%20on%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_60_2%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2260%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EDarkness%20as%20black%20as%20night%20covers%20all%20the%20nations%20of%20the%20earth%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebut%20the%20glory%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20rises%20and%20appears%20over%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_60_3%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2260%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20nations%20will%20come%20to%20your%20light%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Emighty%20kings%20will%20come%20to%20see%20your%20radiance.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_60_4%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2260%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BLook%20and%20see%2C%20for%20everyone%20is%20coming%20home!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EYour%20sons%20are%20coming%20from%20distant%20lands%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eyour%20little%20daughters%20will%20be%20carried%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_60_5%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2260%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EYour%20eyes%20will%20shine%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20your%20heart%20will%20thrill%20with%20joy%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Efor%20merchants%20from%20around%20the%20world%20will%20come%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThey%20will%20bring%20you%20the%20wealth%20of%20many%20lands.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_60_6%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2260%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EVast%20caravans%20of%20camels%20will%20converge%20on%20you%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethe%20camels%20of%20Midian%20and%20Ephah.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThe%20people%20of%20Sheba%20will%20bring%20gold%20and%20frankincense%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20will%20come%20worshiping%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_60_7%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2260%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20flocks%20of%20Kedar%20will%20be%20given%20to%20you%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20rams%20of%20Nebaioth%20will%20be%20brought%20for%20my%20altars.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EI%20will%20accept%20their%20offerings%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20I%20will%20make%20my%20Temple%20glorious.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_60_8%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2260%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAnd%20what%20do%20I%20see%20flying%20like%20clouds%20to%20Israel%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Elike%20doves%20to%20their%20nests%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_60_9%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2260%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20are%20ships%20from%20the%20ends%20of%20the%20earth%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efrom%20lands%20that%20trust%20in%20me%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eled%20by%20the%20great%20ships%20of%20Tarshish.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20are%20bringing%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20home%20from%20far%20away%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ecarrying%20their%20silver%20and%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20will%20honor%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethe%20Holy%20One%20of%20Israel%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20he%20has%20filled%20you%20with%20splendor.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_60_10%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2260%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BForeigners%20will%20come%20to%20rebuild%20your%20towns%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20their%20kings%20will%20serve%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EFor%20though%20I%20have%20destroyed%20you%20in%20my%20anger%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EI%20will%20now%20have%20mercy%20on%20you%20through%20my%20grace.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_60_11%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2260%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EYour%20gates%20will%20stay%20open%20day%20and%20night%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eto%20receive%20the%20wealth%20of%20many%20la